description:
Veep, Veep! Make way for the brilliant and talented Tony Hale (Veep, Arrested Development), joining Anna and Sim today to chat about…

  • The Five Love Languages
  • Pranks & Scary Movies
  • The range of “Fuck You”
  • Francis the Ferret
  • VEEP
  • Whiskey and Ghee

Catch Tony on Netflix in A Series of Unfortunate Events, on HBO in VEEP, and in the upcoming Toy Story 4!

Join us on Thursday as Tony and Anna talk to callers!

Follow us!

Anna Faris: @annakfaris

Unqualified: @unqualified

Tony Hale: @MrTonyHale
